.subsubsection Colours

The main colour schema of EasyGP can simply be changed in the 
.xref User Preferences 
section, by selecting the 'Fonts and Colours' panel. Here you can use your mouse to click anywhere in the colour spectrum shown below, or, by grabbing the little white circle shown here, move dynamically around the colour chart to change the colours on the fly.

